summary: OH MY GOSH IVE FOUND SOMEONE ELSE WHO LOVES BOTH DOCTOR WHO AND STAR WARS AND THE CLONE WARS SERIES TOO WE STAN AHSOKA...
question: OH MY GOSH IVE FOUND SOMEONE ELSE WHO LOVES BOTH DOCTOR WHO AND STAR WARS AND THE CLONE WARS SERIES TOO WE STAN AHSOKA AJSJDBFJFKEKS CAN WE BE FRIENDS
answer:
We can absolutely be friends. 

Though I’m not sure we’re THAT rare of a species. Honestly I’m just a huge science fiction fan so you give me aliens and I am THERE (which is why in addition to loving Star Wars and Doctor Who I also love Star Trek (TNG, DS9 and Discovery) and Stargate (both SG-1 and Atlantis)). 

And yes Ahsoka is the best. And in my opinion the best decision they made was introducing her to the universe, because without her presence I don’t think I could have watched The Clone Wars, it would have been too depressing. 

I mean it hurt anyway. Watching and getting to know Rex and Cody and Fives was absolutely heartbreaking. Watching all those smiling younglings was still a punch to the gut. But Ahsoka was the show’s ray of hope. 

And this universe needs all the hope it can get.
